cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper deals with deep learning models for 3D biomedical segmentation, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of convolutional neural networks and LSTM networks also suggests that the paper could be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on multi-modal MRI data suggests that the paper could also be categorized under neural engineering (cs.NE) and multimedia (cs.MM).
